[00:02.96]The hovercraft | 气垫船
[00:10.31]What is a hovercraft riding on when it is in motion? | 气垫船开动时，它骑在什么上面？
[00:16.55]Many strange new means of transport have been developed in our century, | 本世纪人们发明了许多稀奇古怪的交通工具，
