[00:27.29]In 1953, a former electronics engineer in his fifties, Christopher Cockerell, | 1953年，一位50多岁、曾任电子工程师的克里斯托弗·科克雷尔，
[00:35.44]who had turned to boat-building on the Norfolk Broads, | 他已转行在诺福克湖区制造船只，
